OL,6,FWelsh Rugby Union CEO Abi Tierney has
OL,7,Fbeen diagnosed with cancer.
OL,9,FA statement from the WRU confirmed
OL,10,Fthat Tierney will be stepping away
OL,11,Ffrom her duties at the business from
OL,12,FAugust 22 to undergo treatment.
OL,14,FIn a statement, she said: "This has
OL,15,Fnot been an easy decision, but it is
OL,16,Fone I must make to focus fully on my
OL,17,Fhealth and recovery.
