OL,3,CWelsh Rugby Union CEO Abi Tierney has
OL,4,Cbeen diagnosed with cancer
OL,6,F"I am grateful for the support I have
OL,7,Falready received from my family,
OL,8,Ffriends, and colleagues, and I am
OL,9,Fconfident in the team's ability to
OL,10,Fcontinue our work during my absence.
OL,12,F"I kindly ask for understanding and
OL,13,Fprivacy during this time."
OL,15,FTierney will continue to fulfil her
OL,16,Frole until the end of next week as the
OL,17,FWRU prepares to launch its formal
OL,18,Fconsultation over a complete
OL,19,Frestructuring of the professional game.
