OL,3,CWelsh Rugby Union CEO Abi Tierney has
OL,4,Cbeen diagnosed with cancer
OL,6,FYesterday, Tierney's executive team
OL,7,Ftook their proposals to the WRU Board
OL,8,Fregarding what the landscape of rugby
OL,9,Fin Wales should look like moving
OL,10,Fforward.
OL,12,FNext week, the proposals are due to be
OL,13,Fmade public, with key stakeholders -
OL,14,Fnamely clubs, players, supporters
OL,15,Fgroups and sponsors - then having an
OL,16,Fopportunity to voice their opinions.
OL,18,FTierney will stay on to see those
OL,19,Fproposals go public before stepping
OL,20,Faway.
